17
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,040
Director.

18
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:37,360
This is Zhang Zhun, here to audition.

19
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,640
Hi, Director Chen.

20
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,680
I'm Zhang Zhun.

21
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,560
I studied at the New Arts Academy of Drama.

22
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,136
I'm currently signed with
Xingyao Entertainment.

23
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,360
