24
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,320
Small face.

25
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,360
Very boyish.

26
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,160
Doesn't match your real age, though.

27
00:03:52,320 --> 00:03:52,800
Director Chen,

28
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,280
