42
00:04:17,280 --> 00:04:18,520
My lips are numb from kissing.

43
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,440
Mr. Zhen.

44
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,880
Want some water?

45
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,160
Are we casting,

46
