49
00:04:56,320 --> 00:04:57,520
Throwing a fit again?

50
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:59,920
Just like cutie Qin when she was young.

51
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,040
Mr. Zhen,

52
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,200
this is Zhang Zhun, here to audition.

53
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,680
Hi, Mr. Zhen. Nice seeing you again.

54
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:09,880
Have we met?

55
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,400
Oh.

56
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:12,120
It's been seven or eight years.

57
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:13,696
Totally fair if you don't remember.

58
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,680
I was the female lead's
stunt double in "Zou Ma."

59
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:16,840
Oh?

60
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,720
Not enough action for the female leads now,

61
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,600
so you wanna try the male lead's

62
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,000
drama scenes?

63
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:30,160
Mr. Zhen,

64
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:31,880
you two go way back.

65
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:34,726
Back when you debuted in "North Peak"
as the second male lead,

66
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:37,800
that girl thief you chased
down the whole street,

67
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,040
that was him.

68
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,680
I don't remember stuff like that.

69
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:42,960
Director Chen,

70
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,000
