76
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,800
Ten minutes.

77
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:03,840
Go ahead.

78
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,120
Okay.

79
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,240
Sorry, I don't

80
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:40,320
Your character does.

81
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:03,840
Mr. Zhen,

82
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,880
before I came, I worked out a few...

83
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,920
If you can't keep up with
my acting, just get out.

84
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,840
Fine.

85
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,120
Then let's start.

86
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,400
Wait.

87
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,440
I'm not ready yet.

88
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,080
Never done intimate scenes?

89
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,320
No...

90
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,400
Not this kind.

91
00:07:29,920 --> 00:07:30,920
Then...

92
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,080
