93
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,480
Aren't we gonna talk about the roles?

94
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:49,640
What's there to talk about?

95
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:51,440
We don't have to kiss, right?

96
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,000
A hug could work too.

97
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,280
Director,

98
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,880
