111
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:35,400
Keep these one's audition clips.

112
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,440
Sure, Director.

113
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:40,440
Why are you squirming?

114
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,600
We're rolling.

115
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,160
Action.

116
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,456
More tension, more emotion.

117
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:49,480
Push it further.

118
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,480
Pretend it's Danyi's tongue.

119
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:11,640
But...

120
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,520
Danyi doesn't smoke.

121
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,440
Mr. Zhen is even better this time.

122
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,720
Oscar-worthy as always.

123
00:09:19,400 --> 00:09:20,560
Zhang's still a little off.

124
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,240
Yes, yes.

125
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,080
That's it.

126
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,480
Keep going.

127
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,200
Good.

128
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,520
They've gotten into the groove fast,
and it's getting better and better.

129
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,800
