142
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:49,320
Oh, okay, okay.

143
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,496
Please send me your location.

144
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:51,560
I'll go pick you up later.

145
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:52,760
Hold on.

146
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:53,280
Mr. Zhang,

147
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:53,880
So,

148
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:56,120
