152
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:02,840
Okay, thanks.

153
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,520
Thanks for your hard work.

154
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,160
I'll head out then.

155
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,280
Mm-hmm.

156
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,320
Hey,

157
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:07,760
wait a sec.

158
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:08,920
I'll come pick you up in a bit.

159
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:09,440
Okay, okay.

160
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,600
Okay, hang on, hang on.

161
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:46,120
[Xie Danyi]

162
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:50,320
Hello, Zhun.

163
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,360
You're still up?

164
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,160
I couldn't sleep

165
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,200
without your update.

166
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:55,240
How was it.

167
00:12:55,280 --> 00:12:56,280
You home yet?

168
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,840
Not yet.

169
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,600
So late.

170
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:01,520
On my way back, Pang called me.

171
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,320
Said a friend was coming by
the prop warehouse.

172
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:05,800
He was stuck on set,

173
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:07,640
so I came to cover for him.

174
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,560
You're too nice.

175
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:12,720
So how'd it go today?

176
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,920
Based on the director's reaction,

177
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:16,160
probably okay.

178
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,680
But a lot of people auditioned.

179
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,520
Gotta wait for the result.

180
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,720
Whatever.

181
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:23,960
Hope they pick someone else.

182
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,440
I don't want guys groping you all day.

183
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,720
I'm simply too old for that.

184
00:13:30,120 --> 00:13:31,440
Says who?

185
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:35,960
My parents called again today.

186
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,960
Asking when they'll meet your parents.

187
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,680
A-Zhun,

188
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:42,640
I don't want to pressure you,

189
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:45,240
but I'm at that age now.

190
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,360
Danyi,

191
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,400
give me a little more time.

192
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,720
This year,

193
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,440
if it still doesn't happen,

194
00:13:55,160 --> 00:13:56,600
I'll think about quitting acting.

195
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:01,600
The guy picking up the props is here.

196
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:03,040
I gotta go.

197
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,080
Bye.

198
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:16,400
I just lost a bit of that boyish spark

199
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:25,240
and suddenly there's gray at my tempes.

200
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:49,920
Lin

201
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,080
thanks for recommending me.

202
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,760
That's how I got this audition.

203
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,280
Lin, please

204
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,800
put in another word with the crew.

205
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:04,040
I really need this shot.

206
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,560
[Lin, please]

207
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,976
[put in another word with the crew.]

208
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,120
[I really need this shot.]

209
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:12,920
Dating?

210
00:16:12,960 --> 00:16:13,960
Fine by me.

211
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:15,720
But hide it better!

212
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,776
You know how many
deals you've already lost?

213
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:19,120
You wanna throw your career away?

214
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,320
Sending a legal notice is just useless.

215
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,840
Tell him again.

216
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,560
No dating inside the company.

217
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:27,440
Tell him to stop asking for trouble.

218
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:34,360
Qin...

219
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,880
How many times have I told you?

220
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,600
Call me sis!

221
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,000
Sis Qin.

222
00:16:42,360 --> 00:16:43,480
I don't get it.

223
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,120
Director Chen's gay art film

224
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:48,760
