and CP incubator.

225
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:52,440
So how did Zhang Zhun land the spot?

226
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:54,680
Oh my God, sis.

227
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,480
Isn't it good your guy got picked?

228
00:16:56,760 --> 00:16:57,760
Sure,

229
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,240
but...

230
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:00,880
since when does

231
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,720
free lunch just fall from the sky?

232
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:04,880
Zhang Zhun just doesn't have star power.

233
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:06,800
The company's already given up pushing him.

234
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:08,920
And this time...

235
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,520
Zhen Xin picked him himself.

236
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:19,640
Come on, sis.

237
00:17:19,680 --> 00:17:20,680
No way.

238
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:34,320
Why the long face?

239
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,880
Got chewed out again?

240
00:17:38,560 --> 00:17:39,696
The Douban Forum hate thread on me

241
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:41,080
is over a thousand comments now.

242
00:17:41,600 --> 00:17:42,736
They keep saying do it if you can,

243
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:43,760
and if not, get lost.

244
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:46,360
That  accident on set
was a misunderstanding.

245
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:47,760
Didn't I already explain that?

246
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:48,840
All right.

247
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:50,440
Sweetheart,

248
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:51,840
it's over.

249
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,240
Here,

250
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:53,600
pick one.

251
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,600
What's that supposed to mean?

252
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:59,840
I've got you the Chen
Zhengsen's male lead...

253
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:02,360
but still don't have his scene partner set.

254
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:04,760
These are all from our company.

255
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:06,480
Pick whichever one you like,

256
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:07,800
and I'll send him to audition.

257
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:19,720
So now I'm supposed to mentor a
newbie and let him ride my coattails?

258
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,840
Oh, come on.

259
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,080
You're already huge.

260
00:18:26,480 --> 00:18:28,080
Cut me some slack.

261
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:31,000
I know you're only in your twenties

262
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:33,200
and just won Best Actor
with a promising future.

263
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:34,800
The company doing this

264
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,320
is a little much.

265
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:38,760
But trying to cash in now

266
00:18:39,280 --> 00:18:40,280
is normal too.

267
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,440
Just think of it as

268
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:44,560
payback for all these
years I busted my ass for you.

269
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:45,280
Deal?

270
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:46,160
Come on.

271
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:47,520
Pick one.

272
00:19:13,960 --> 00:19:14,960
Here.

273
00:19:19,360 --> 00:19:20,360
You sure?

274
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:23,360
Be serious, okay?

275
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:25,000
Why'd you pick this ugly kid?

276
00:19:30,800 --> 00:19:31,800
No.

277
00:19:31,831 --> 00:19:33,176
[Zhang Zhun]

278
00:19:33,240 --> 00:19:34,240
Him.

279
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:40,160
I don't get why Zhen Xin picked him either.

280
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,840
They barely even know each other, right?

281
00:19:47,560 --> 00:19:49,600
Think maybe he pissed Zhen Xin off before?

282
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:54,680
Then that ugly kid's in for it on set.

283
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,240
Still,

284
00:19:57,320 --> 00:19:58,880
it really is a chance.

285
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:01,520
Well then,

286
00:20:01,840 --> 00:20:02,840
good luck to both of you.

287
00:20:09,119 --> 00:20:10,699
[Five days later]

288
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:14,000
I got beef rolls...

289
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,480
as well.

290
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,960
And your favorite shiitake beef sauce.

291
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,280
Beef roll.

292
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,840
Shiitake Beef Sauce.

293
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:28,040
That's it.

294
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:31,040
Besides getting hot pot ready... [Message from the
AD saying he got the part and needs to fly out]

295
00:20:31,200 --> 00:20:31,720
Danyi.

296
00:20:32,080 --> 00:20:33,080
I got the part.

297
00:20:33,680 --> 00:20:34,680
Really?

298
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:35,640
That's amazing.

299
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,600
Then we really have to celebrate tonight.

300
00:20:36,640 --> 00:20:37,040
I can't.

301
00:20:37,200 --> 00:20:38,200
There's no time.

302
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:39,760
The crew wants me there tomorrow.

303
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,496
I have to fly to Coconut City right away.

304
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:42,520
Danyi...

305
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,160
Okay.

306
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:43,920
Don't worry about me.

307
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:45,160
I'll be fine.

308
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:46,200
Go pack.

309
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:46,640
Okay.

310
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,520
I'll have the food sent over.

311
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:49,640
We'll save hot pot for later.

312
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,040
When I wrap and come back,

313
00:20:51,080 --> 00:20:52,400
I'll have a proper meal with you.

314
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:53,600
Okay I'll wait.

315
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:56,880
Just scan this code.

316
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,160
Do you need a bag?

317
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:01,840
[He spent 163 yuan with a
a remaining balance of 1,735.85.]

318
00:21:01,880 --> 00:21:02,640
No bag, thanks.

319
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,840
OK.

320
00:21:05,426 --> 00:21:06,426
This is yours too, right?

321
00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:07,560
Yes, together.

322
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:09,840
I'm a member.

323
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,000
Can you add up my points?

324
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:17,320
Okay.

325
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:19,255
Okay, I know.

326
00:21:19,280 --> 00:21:20,280
All right, got it.

327
00:21:20,400 --> 00:21:21,400
Okay, thanks.

328
00:21:23,040 --> 00:21:24,040
I'll follow up again.

329
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:25,640
Okay.

330
00:21:36,360 --> 00:21:38,120
And that project we talked about last time,

331
00:21:38,593 --> 00:21:39,153
is it a go?

332
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,696
[Xie Danyi updating him
and expressing concern]

333
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:41,880
Good. Then it should be fine.

334
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:43,320
Okay, thanks.

335
00:21:43,360 --> 00:21:44,776
[She's telling him about the on-set
assault, and warning him about Zhen Xin.]

336
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:45,600
That's alright.

337
00:21:45,760 --> 00:21:46,200
Yeah,

338
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:47,680
So that's it.

339
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:48,920
Seven years ago, on the set of "Zou Ma"

340
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:49,360
Cut.

341
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,200
Mr. Zhen nailed it in one take.

342
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,320
That's a wrap for today.

343
00:22:24,360 --> 00:22:25,360
Thank you Mr. Zhen.

344
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:30,400
Bro, let me borrow your umbrella.

345
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,120
The top leads don't have one.

346
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:34,360
Thanks.

347
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:40,800
Carefully, Mr. Zhen.

348
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,960
Gossip sites love blowing this stuff up.

349
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,480
Don't let it get to you.

350
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:58,800
I'll take care of myself.

351
00:23:01,520 --> 00:23:02,040
Lin.

352
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:03,680
Nervous?

353
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,960
Are you close with Zhen Xin?

354
00:23:09,280 --> 00:23:10,280
Huh?

355
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:12,000
No.

356
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:14,720
I just doubled for an
actress in one of his scenes.

357
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,240
I know that.

358
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,400
Anything else?

359
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:18,400
Did you...

360
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,680
ever piss him off?

361
00:23:20,320 --> 00:23:20,760
Talk trash about him,

362
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:21,800
or

363
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:23,120
steal his girlfriend?

364
00:23:24,760 --> 00:23:25,120
Lin.

365
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:27,120
I don't even have his WeChat.

366
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:31,680
Did something happen?

367
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:33,280
No, no.

368
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,440
Just asking.

369
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:39,160
Then why's he being so nice?

370
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:41,600
Listen,

371
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,680
remember this.

372
00:23:43,440 --> 00:23:45,160
Zhen Xin is the top guy in our company.

373
00:23:46,319 --> 00:23:47,319
On set,

374
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:48,040
keep your eyes open.

375
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,320
You know what I mean, right?

376
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:50,840
Play nice when you need to,

377
00:23:51,120 --> 00:23:52,560
and stroke his ego when you have to.

378
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,640
Just don't offend him.

379
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:55,200
Okay?

380
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:56,480
Got it.

381
00:23:56,520 --> 00:23:57,520
All right, get some rest.

382
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,480
Mr. Zhang.

383
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:25,520
Thank you for your work. Come on in.

384
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:30,640
Mr. Zhang,

385
00:24:30,840 --> 00:24:31,840
good to see you again.

386
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:33,680
I'm Zhao Chen, the casting AD on this film.

387
00:24:34,120 --> 00:24:35,616
You'll coordinate with me from now on.

388
00:24:35,640 --> 00:24:35,880
Okay.

389
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:37,160
I'll get your suitcase.

390
00:24:37,320 --> 00:24:37,640
No, it's okay.

391
00:24:37,760 --> 00:24:38,760
I got it.

392
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:40,216
It's fine. The elevator's over there.

393
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,240
Okay.

394
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:47,400
Here's your key card.

395
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:49,320
So...

396
00:24:49,360 --> 00:24:52,000
We officially start shooting
in half a month.

397
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:53,160
So,

398
00:24:53,200 --> 00:24:55,280
right now, only you and
Mr. Zhen are here early.

399
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:57,600
You're both in room 3804.

400
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,880
It's a suite.

401
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,240
Both of us?

402
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:04,320
Right.

403
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:06,480
Since this film...

404
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:10,000
starts with intimate scenes,

405
00:25:10,560 --> 00:25:13,080
the director arranged
for you two to stay together.

406
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:16,320
He wants you to get comfortable early,

407
00:25:16,520 --> 00:25:17,840
and settle into the roles sooner.

408
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:25,880
Mr. Zhang,

409
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,360
do your best.

410
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,040
You should rest up first.

411
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:29,760
I'll get going.

412
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,000
Okay.

413
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:31,720
See you tomorrow, Director.

414
00:25:31,800 --> 00:25:32,800
Okay, bye.

415
00:25:54,760 --> 00:25:55,760
Mr. Zhen?

416
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,760
Mr. Zhen?

417
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:25,640
Mr. Zhen?

418
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:28,920
Mr. Zhen?

419
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,200
Stop right there!

420
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,560
Why the hell are you here?

421
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:14,400
Mr. Zhen,

422
00:27:14,840 --> 00:27:16,120
I didn't know you were in there.

423
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,240
I rang the bell,

424
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,040
and nobody answered.

425
00:27:18,080 --> 00:27:19,400
I thought you hadn't arrived yet.

426
00:27:20,360 --> 00:27:22,280
What the hell does
that have to do with anything?

427
00:27:22,680 --> 00:27:23,680
Answer me.

428
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:26,680
Why are you in my room?

429
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:30,760
It's my room too.

430
00:27:31,240 --> 00:27:32,240
What?

431
00:27:32,760 --> 00:27:33,520
Our film

432
00:27:33,560 --> 00:27:34,640
is kind of special, right?

433
00:27:35,320 --> 00:27:35,840
The director...

434
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:37,240
the AD said

435
00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:39,160
he wants us to build chemistry fast.

436
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:41,880
So we're staying together
before shooting starts,

437
00:27:42,080 --> 00:27:43,440
to help us get into character.

438
00:27:44,800 --> 00:27:46,040
Didn’t he tell you?

439
00:27:47,086 --> 00:27:48,873
[A bunch of missed calls from the director]

440
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:50,680
Fuck.

441
00:27:51,120 --> 00:27:52,120
My phone was on silent.

442
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,680
Even if we are staying together,

443
00:27:57,040 --> 00:27:58,280
what the hell are you doing?

444
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:02,800
I was gonna take a shower...

445
00:28:08,000 --> 00:28:09,696
A ridiculous request like
this from the crew,

446
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:11,040
and you don't know how to say no?

447
00:28:11,393 --> 00:28:12,393
I...

448
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:15,040
I do what the director says.

449
00:28:16,320 --> 00:28:17,320
Pathetic.

450
00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:19,320
I'm going to talk to Chen Zhengsen.

451
00:28:52,040 --> 00:28:53,040
So, Mr. Zhen...

452
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:56,600
Did the director say yes?

453
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,440
I thought it over.

454
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,280
We're both actors.

455
00:29:03,720 --> 00:29:05,000
For the film, for the roles,

456
00:29:05,800 --> 00:29:07,840
building chemistry andstaying
immersed makes sense.

457
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:10,120
You don't have a problem with that, do you?

458
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:11,320
No...

459
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:12,360
No problem.

460
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:14,880
Then pick one.

461
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,640
This is...

462
00:29:21,266 --> 00:29:22,546
A flash drive from the director.

463
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:27,440
He needs us to watch
every movie together. In bed.

464
00:29:29,200 --> 00:29:30,280
Is that really necessary?

465
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:34,080
You think you're that good?

466
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:41,480
Read the script and you'll know why.

467
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:56,080
[The way he yanked his pants off...

468
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:58,200
the leg thrown over his shoulder...]

469
00:30:00,960 --> 00:30:03,000
[Does that feel good? Say
it! Does that feel good?]

470
00:30:07,760 --> 00:30:08,760
Do we really have to...

471
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:10,160
act all of it out?

472
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:12,760
I'm in the inner room.

473
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,600
Come in and talk.

474
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:28,080
When you're filming,

475
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:30,160
you just leave your stuff
on the bed like this?

476
00:30:30,720 --> 00:30:31,840
I usually have an assistant.

477
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,720
But this time, since we're here early,

478
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,080
I'm not allowed to bring one.

479
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,560
So your assistant cleans up at home too?

480
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:41,560
My girlfriend does.

481
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:46,960
Didn't the company just say a few days ago
that you were single?

482
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,560
The lonely heartthrob and all that?

483
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,400
What, I can't date in secret?

484
00:30:54,800 --> 00:30:55,800
Sure.

485
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:56,920
Of course you can.

486
00:30:57,280 --> 00:30:57,680
Relax.

487
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:59,160
I'll act like I know nothing.

488
00:31:48,760 --> 00:31:49,760
I picked you this time.

489
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:53,280
Really?

490
00:31:55,320 --> 00:31:56,320
Thank you, Mr. Zhen.

491
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,600
I didn't expect youto give me this shot.

492
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:01,360
No need to thank me.

493
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,120
I just grabbed your résumé at random.

494
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:14,400
So,

495
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,400
how are you going to thank me?

496
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:22,000
You pick

497
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,760
which side of the bed you wanna sleep.

498
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,680
So, what'd you think of the script?

499
00:32:37,280 --> 00:32:38,280
I think...

500
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,240
it's really nuanced.

501
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:41,760
Yeah.

502
00:32:42,360 --> 00:32:43,920
This movie has a lot of sexual tension.

503
00:32:45,080 --> 00:32:46,080
We really do...

504
00:32:47,520 --> 00:32:48,920
need to build some chemistry.

505
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,640
Yeah.

506
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:52,160
So,

507
00:32:52,606 --> 00:32:53,846
pick one and let's watch it.

508
00:32:58,560 --> 00:32:59,960
Just watching won't do much.

509
00:33:01,400 --> 00:33:03,240
Do you know how to
play scenes like this well?

510
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:07,400
Then let's...

511
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:09,480
watch them together tonight,

512
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,400
and tomorrow morning,

513
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,120
we can practice.

514
00:33:23,560 --> 00:33:24,560
Um...

515
00:33:24,759 --> 00:33:26,279
The rest of the time is personal time.

516
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,640
I do my workouts,

517
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:28,840
you do your thing.

518
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,560
We're just coworkers.

519
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,640
What else would we be?

520
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:36,320
It's not like we're actually gay.

521
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,480
Oh, and...

522
00:33:49,520 --> 00:33:51,360
in bed, I usually take
the lead a little more.

523
00:33:51,560 --> 00:33:54,040
You don’t need to tell me
about you and you girlfriend.

524
00:33:57,120 --> 00:33:58,120
I meant...

525
00:34:01,480 --> 00:34:02,480
with you.

526
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,360
From now.

527
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:44,240
Do not take other's umbrella casually.

528
00:37:44,600 --> 00:37:46,120
It's not that matter，just a bit.

529
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:59,200
Someone took his umbrella, got soaked...

530
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,720
And he's squatting there,
eating likehe's happy as hell.

531
00:38:02,640 --> 00:38:03,640
What's his name?

532
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,320
No idea.
